fields.name: Cheese Cake
fields.description: An amazing dessert made with a soft fresh cheese; it could be cottage cheese, cream cheese, quark or ricotta, eggs, and sugar.

fields.name: Carrot Cake
fields.description: A tasty fluffy and moist cake that is commonly served with a chocolate ganache topping.

fields.name: Chocolate Cake
fields.description: A beautiful looking and yummy cake flavored with melted chocolate, cocoa powder, or both.

fields.name: Red Velvet Cake
fields.description: A nice colored red, crimson, or scarlet-colored layer cake, layered with ermine icing or cream cheese icing.

fields.name: Butter Cake
fields.description: A cake made with butter as a main ingredient, along with sugar, eggs, flour, and leavening agents like baking powder or baking soda.
